<p>The suspect then repeatedly screamed 'Get out, Get out of here you f****** n*****!' 'What is your problem?' the jogger said before continuing her run</p>

<p>The bottle is heard shattering on the ground and the victim turned around confused after the glass smashed by her feet. </p>

